ing the signal.";i:51;s:70:"The receiving eye will light steady green with it is properly aligned.";i:52;s:95:"If both sensors are lighting up yellow then you have 2 sending sensors and no receiving sensor.";i:53;s:63:"The lights on your sensors indicate if theyre working properly.";i:54;s:91:"Most garage door sensors will have one yellow and one green light when theyre in alignment.";i:55;s:62:"Genie garage door openers may also have a green and red light.";i:56;s:52:"All you need to do is check if the lights are solid.";}}